lity of the Six Paths Sage Mode. To put it simply, the Six Paths Sage Mode is a power that Hagoromo Otsutsuki gifted to him for having a strong will and the guts to never give up. This power is quite similar to Sage Mode in that it makes use of natural energy, or Senjutsu chakra, however, the scale at which it allows him to perform techniques is much bigger.</p> <p style="text-align: center,"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline,">Limited to 300 units!!</span></strong></p>$$DESC$$,
